A military plane suspected to be that of the Nigerian Air Force (NAF) has crashed around the Kaduna International Airport. The plane, which crashed around 6pm on Friday, according to a source, exploded and got burnt completely. A competent source from the Airport told The Nation all the crew members and passengers numbering 12 died in the crash. Though, there has not been any official statement from the Armed Forces, eyewitnesses suspected the crew lost control of the aircraft due to sudden change of weather before the evening rain in Kaduna Details shortlyâ€¦